0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:25:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7af747d885bf7d04bfe4999801c0b487195fee60","tid":180653,"uid":34411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:27:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26eb86c48d8750fa56a42d6f8054829f6eaedcab","tid":180653,"uid":40905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:02:18.000Z","msg":"單挑S8? 搞到我好期待，hold住唔買u ultra<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現身安兔兔  HTC U 向 Galaxy S8 挑機<br />\n<br />\n雖然並非首部公佈，但 Galaxy S8、S8+ 相信是首批上市的 Snapdragon 835 手機。當 S8 上市後，其他使用 Snapdragon 835 的手機亦會陸續推出，其中一部很可能是 HTC U。日前 HTC U 就被發現出現於跑分網站安兔兔，採用的處理器正是 Snapdragon 835。<br />\n<br />\n報導指 HTC U 就是流傳已久的 HTC Ocean，根據安兔兔的資料，HTC U 擁有 1,440 x 2,560 解像度，相信為 5.5 吋的螢幕，搭配 Snapdragon 835 處理器、4GB RAM 和 64GB 儲存，前後相機分別為 12MP 和 16MP，而預載系統則為 Android 7.1.1。HTC U 的最大賣點其實並非它的處理器，而是擁有辨認手勢動作的 Sense Touch 螢幕邊緣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2017-03/31/207914/uniqlo_1_ee9abb11f8deb67a88d0aba900a20741.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2017-03%2F31%2F207914%2Funiqlo_1_ee9abb11f8deb67a88d0aba900a20741.jpg&h=fdc2179c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4542/207914/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4542%2F207914%2F1%2F&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIcywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=e7cbb7c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4542/207914/1/</a>"},{"pid":"61be014b155767e038faf5e5f2907b18d83b2d09","tid":180653,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:19:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾好都冇用，個連登app都唔夠iOS版好用。</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">D</span>個真</blockquote><br />\n呢"},{"pid":"84f3fba8362bec9965769485901a7b4f726b1eb0","tid":180653,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy